---

<BaseLayout
  title="Drive-Thru Near Nashville, TN | Coffee & Food to Go"
  description="The Local Drive-Thru in Centerville is just 45 minutes from Nashville. Fresh coffee, quick breakfast, and lunch without leaving your car. Perfect for commuters and busy professionals."
  keywords="drive thru near Nashville, drive through Nashville area, quick coffee Nashville, fast breakfast"
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>Drive-Thru Near Nashville</h1>
      <p>Fresh Coffee & Quick Food. 45 Minutes South of the City.</p>
      <a href="https://www.clover.com/online-ordering/the-local-drivethru-centerville" class="hero-cta">Order Ahead</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="container py-4">
    <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <ol>
        <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
        <li><span>Drive-Thru Near Nashville</span></li>
      </ol>
    </nav>

    <section class="location-intro">
      <h2>The Local Drive-Thru for Nashville Commuters</h2>
      <p>
        You're driving south from Nashville on your way to Franklin, Columbia, or anywhere south. You want coffee that tastes like someone cared. Not a gas station cup. Not a chain drive-thru coffee. Real espresso pulled 5 minutes ago. We're 45 minutes from downtown Nashville, and plenty of people make the trip south just to stop by. Stop by on your way through. You'll get it.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="content-grid">
      <div class="content-block">
        <h3>Easy Drive from Nashville</h3>
        <p><strong>Distance:</strong> 45 minutes from downtown Nashville</p>
        <p><strong>Route:</strong> I-65 South → Dickson Exit → TN-100 South → Centerville</p>
        <p><strong>No Detour Needed:</strong> We're on the way if you're heading south anyway</p>
        <p>
          Comfortable drive. Good music time. Your coffee's ready when you arrive because you'll order ahead on Clover. By the time you pull up, we've got your latte or cappuccino waiting.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h3>Why Nashville Drivers Choose Us</h3>
        <ul style="margin-left: 1.5rem;">
          <li>Real espresso. No burnt coffee. No shortcuts.</li>
          <li>Order ahead on Clover. Pick up in 5 minutes.</li>
          <li>Perfect for the commute. Fresh coffee to keep you awake.</li>
          <li>Breakfast sandwiches and pastries. Better than gas station food.</li>
          <li>Quick lunch if you're heading south for business.</li>
          <li>Open 5am on weekdays. We're here when Nashville's still asleep.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h3>What to Order</h3>
        <ul style="margin-left: 1.5rem;">
          <li><strong>Morning Commute:</strong> Espresso or cappuccino + fresh pastry</li>
          <li><strong>Breakfast Run:</strong> Breakfast sandwich + latte</li>
          <li><strong>Lunch Break:</strong> Panini or wrap + cold brew</li>
          <li><strong>Afternoon Pick-Me-Up:</strong> Americano or latte + muffin</li>
          <li><strong>Weekend Trip:</strong> Whatever you want. No rush.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h3>Hours & Location</h3>
        <p>
          <strong>Monday-Friday:</strong> 5 AM - 6 PM<br />
          <strong>Saturday:</strong> 7 AM - 6 PM<br />
          <strong>Sunday:</strong> Closed
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Address:</strong> 1171 TN-100<br />
          Centerville, TN 37033<br />
          <strong>Phone:</strong> <a href="tel:(931)729-4821">(931) 729-4821</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="testimonials">
      <h2>What Nashville Drivers Say</h2>
      <div class="testimonial-cards">
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <p>\"I drive from Nashville to Franklin twice a week. The Local Drive-Thru is my pit stop. Order coffee on Clover before I leave Nashville, pick it up 45 minutes later. Still hot. Still perfect.\"</p>
          <p><strong>- Mark (Nashville to Franklin)</strong></p>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <p>\"Morning commute from Nashville. I used to get gas station coffee. Now I add 10 minutes and get real espresso. Worth it every time.\"</p>
          <p><strong>- Patricia (Commuter)</strong></p>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <p>\"Nashville-based sales guy. This drive-thru is on my route south. Fresh coffee every time. Beats anything in the city.\"</p>
          <p><strong>- James (Sales)</strong></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="faq-section">
      <h2>Questions from Nashville Drivers</h2>
      <div class="faq-items">
        <details class="faq-item" open>
          <summary class="faq-question">
            <span>How far from Nashville is the drive-thru?</span>
            <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>45 minutes from downtown Nashville heading south on I-65. If you're already heading to Franklin, Columbia, or anywhere south, we're right on the way.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question">
            <span>Can I order from Nashville and pick up on the drive?</span>
            <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Absolutely. Use Clover to order before you leave Nashville. Tell us your pickup time. We'll have your coffee ready when you pull up 45 minutes later. Still hot. Still perfect.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question">
            <span>What's the best time to stop from Nashville?</span>
            <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>If you're leaving Nashville early (before 7am), order ahead and we'll have it ready. If you're stopping midday, it's quick any time. Avoid peak commute times (7-8:30am, 12-1pm from Centerville's perspective) if you want instant service.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question">
            <span>Is it worth the drive from Nashville?</span>
            <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>If you're heading south anyway, yes. Real espresso beats gas station coffee every time. If you're making a special trip just for coffee, probably not. But if you're passing through, absolutely stop.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question">
            <span>What if I don't know the route from Nashville?</span>
            <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>GPS to 1171 TN-100, Centerville, TN 37033. Or: I-65 South from Nashville → Dickson Exit → TN-100 South → Centerville. It's straightforward.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question">
            <span>Do you have parking?</span>
            <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Drive-thru lane. You don't park. You pull up, order or pick up your pre-order, and drive away. That's the whole thing.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question">
            <span>Can I eat my coffee inside?</span>
            <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>This is drive-thru only. No seating. No inside option. Take your coffee in the car or to your destination.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question">
            <span>What's your payment situation?</span>
            <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Cash or card at the window. If you order on Clover, you pay online. Easy.</p>
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="why-stop-section">
      <h2>Why Stop When Driving from Nashville</h2>
      <div class="why-grid">
        <div class="why-item">
          <h3>Better Than Gas Station</h3>
          <p>Real espresso. Fresh pastries. Not stale coffee sitting under a heat lamp.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-item">
          <h3>You're Heading That Way Anyway</h3>
          <p>Going south from Nashville? We're basically on your route to Franklin and beyond.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-item">
          <h3>Order Ahead = No Wait</h3>
          <p>Order from Nashville on Clover. Pick up 45 minutes later without stopping.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-item">
          <h3>Quality Matters</h3>
          <p>You'll taste the difference. Good coffee hits different when you're on the road.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section">
      <h2>Next Time You Drive South from Nashville</h2>
      <p>Order on Clover before you leave. We'll have your coffee ready when you arrive.</p>
      <a href="https://www.clover.com/online-ordering/the-local-drivethru-centerville" class="cta-button">Order Now on Clover</a>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .content-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .content-block {
    background: var(--light-gray);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 4px solid #8b4513;
  }

  .content-block h3 {
    margin-top: 0;
    color: var(--dark);
  }

  .content-block a {
    color: #8b4513;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .content-block a:hover {
    color: var(--red);
  }

  .testimonial-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .testimonial-card {
    background: var(--cream);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 4px solid #8b4513;
  }

  .testimonial-card p {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .testimonial-card p:first-child {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text-light);
  }

  .testimonial-card p:last-child {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--dark);
  }

  .why-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .why-item {
    background: var(--light-gray);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .why-item h3 {
    margin-top: 0;
    color: var(--dark);
  }

  .why-item p {
    margin-bottom: 0;
    color: var(--text-light);
  }

  .faq-items {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .faq-item {
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--white);
  }

  .faq-question {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    background: var(--light-gray);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--dark);
    user-select: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .faq-question:hover {
    background: #efefef;
  }

  .toggle-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-left: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .faq-item[open] .toggle-icon {
    transform: rotate(45deg);
  }

  .faq-answer {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--white);
    border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--text-light);
  }

  .cta-section {
    background: var(--light-gray);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .cta-button {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #8b4513;
    color: white;
    padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    transition: background 0.3s ease;
  }

  .cta-button:hover {
    background: #6b3410;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .content-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .testimonial-cards {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .why-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
